The cards of this deck shimmer around the edges. While holding this deck, you can use the following properties:
• {'type': 'item', 'name': 'Deadly Deal', 'entries': ['As an action, you can use this deck to make a ranged spell attack by throwing a spectral card and using Dexterity for the attack roll. The card has a range of 120 feet and deals {@damage 1d8} force damage on a hit.']}
• {'type': 'item', 'name': 'Spray of Cards', 'entries': ["As an action, you can shuffle the deck and cast the {@spell Spray of Cards|BMT} spell at 3rd level from the deck (spell save {@dc 15}). Once the deck has cast the spell, it can't cast the spell again until the next dawn."]}

